00:00:22,733 --> 00:00:23,900
-Yeah.

8
00:00:23,933 --> 00:00:25,900
I guess he would have
been if we kept him alive.

9
00:00:25,933 --> 00:00:28,733
-He was in the ground before
we even sent the ransom note.

